<p>We collect information about you during the account registration process for any of our Services. This information may include, but is not limited to your name, postal address, e-mail address, phone number, credit/debit card details and any other details as might be requested from you for the purpose of registration and/or continued use of our Services.</p>
<p>We may also collect information from you if you request information or customer support.</p>
<p><strong>Additional Information collected:</strong></p>
<p>We may also collect the following information:</p>
<ol>
<li>name, contact information and message if you contact us or participate in a survey, contest or promotion;</li>
