<li>To keep you logged in when you use our website so you are not required to log in every time you visit; and</li>
<li>Remember and update your selections in your bet slip during a live session up to the time of its placement.</li>
</ul>
<p>These cookies do not remember your preferences or username beyond your current visit.</p>
</td>
